Class SchemaElementDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • uk.gov.gchq.gaffer.store.schema.SchemaElementDefinition
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable, ElementDefinition
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    SchemaEdgeDefinition, SchemaEntityDefinition
    public abstract class SchemaElementDefinition
extends Object
implements ElementDefinition
    A SchemaElementDefinition is the representation of a single group in a Schema. Each element needs identifiers and can optionally have properties, an aggregator and a validator.
